# NestJS OpenAPI Rules

## API Documentation

1. Use consistent endpoint naming
2. Implement proper request/response schemas
3. Use TypeScript decorators properly
4. Document all endpoints thoroughly
5. Maintain API versioning

## Schema Management

1. Use proper DTOs
2. Implement proper validation
3. Use appropriate decorators
4. Handle nested schemas properly
5. Maintain schema consistency

## Best Practices

1. Use proper security schemes
2. Implement proper error responses
3. Use appropriate content types
4. Handle file uploads properly
5. Follow OpenAPI best practices

## Documentation

1. Use proper API descriptions
2. Implement proper examples
3. Use appropriate tags
4. Handle deprecated endpoints
5. Maintain documentation up to date 